<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:20px;color:#1a1a2e;">
  Your Approved Submission Was Auto-Refunded
</h2>

<p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;color:#333333;line-height:1.6;">
  Hi {{userName}},
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#333333;line-height:1.6;">
  Our scheduled visibility checks could no longer access the post you
  submitted for <strong>"{{bountyTitle}}"</strong>. The bounty had a
  PostVisibility rule (<strong>{{visibilityRule}}</strong>) requiring
  the post to remain live, so the brand's payment has been
  automatically refunded.
</p>

<!-- Status Badge -->
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:8px 16px;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;background-color:#dc3545;">
      Submission Refunded
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:16px;background-color:#f8f9fa;border-left:4px solid #6c63ff;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;">
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">
        What Happened
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;">
        {{failureReason}}
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">
        Why It Matters
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;">
        Bounties with visibility requirements need the post to stay live
        for their full duration. If the post comes back online and you
        believe this was an error, please reach out to support.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if actionUrl}}
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 16px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color:#6c63ff;border-radius:6px;">
      <a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
        View Submission
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin:16px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#999999;">
  Keep the great work coming — there are plenty more bounties waiting.
</p>
